name: We Are All Connected
description: The life of the universe often gives us surprises. We’ve been prepared to meet some new lines of life. We met our parents, siblings, and environments that shapes our thoughts and personalities. From time to time we have been given the opportunity to meet new people. Technological civilization is no exception. We are easier to encounter with a lot of random things. Until us as an artist with different genres and tastes meet in the same space, even in a virtual space. Thank you for those who read this article, it has become a part of my life. Nothing is coincidence in this world.
